        <h2 class="section-title">
         Admissions on the Road
        </h2>
        <div class="float-left one-half">
         <div class="panel">
          <p>
           IU South Bend admission counselors travel all over the Michiana area for:
          </p>
          <ul>
           <li>
            College/Career fairs for high school students
           </li>
           <li>
            On-the-spot admission decisions at local high schools
           </li>
           <li>
            Events for students
           </li>
          </ul>
