        <h3 class="section-title">
         A recommendation you can make proudly
        </h3>
        <div class="text">
         <p>
          <strong>
           High School Counselors
          </strong>
          , when you refer your high school students to IU South Bend, you can be confident you are recommending an institution that is one of the region’s foremost universities, a campus that offers the complete college experience. We offer more than 100 majors as well as robust graduate and distance learning programs.
         </p>
         <a class="button" href="high-school-counselors/index.html">
